                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9412" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1413</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1522 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贝泰妮溢价并购背后——利好与暗流的交织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Behind the premium acquisition of Betaine: the interweaving of positive and negative factors</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷芳，陈思荣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南贝泰妮生物科技集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">溢价并购；业绩补偿承诺；协同效应；并购风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Premium mergers and acquisitions, performance compensation commitments, synergies, merger and acquisition risks</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021年3月25日，“药妆第一股”成功上市，上市当日贝泰妮股价便暴涨约2.6倍。但好景不长，内外压力促使贝泰妮不得不寻求并购。2023年9月，贝泰妮首次“出手”，以自有资金5.35亿元将悦江投资纳入麾下。双方根据市场法辅以未来现金流折现法，对悦江投资2023年上半年末的净资产9161.31万元进行估值，评估净资产为10亿元，估值增值率为10.92倍。本次交易不仅仅是资本与资源的整合，更是两家企业战略愿景和市场定位的契合。本案例以并购动因为切入点，从溢价并购、业绩补偿承诺等多角度描述了此次并购全过程。通过案例，引导学员思考溢价并购带来的收益与风险、企业并购在战略管理和市场扩展中的应用与影响，同时把握业绩补偿承诺协议在双方交易过程中的促进作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On March 25, 2021, the &quot;first pharmaceutical and cosmetics stock&quot; was successfully listed, and on the day of listing, Betainy&#39;s stock price skyrocketed by about 2.6 times. But the good times didn&#39;t last long, and internal and external pressures forced Betaine to seek mergers and acquisitions. In September 2023, Betainy made its first move by bringing Yuejiang Investment under its umbrella with its own funds of 535 million yuan. Both parties valued Yuejiang Investment&#39;s net assets of 91.6131 million yuan at the end of the first half of 2023 using the market approach supplemented by the discounted future cash flow method, with an estimated net asset value of 1 billion yuan and a valuation appreciation rate of 10.92 times. This transaction is not only the integration of capital and resources, but also the alignment of the strategic vision and market positioning of the two companies. This case study starts from the perspective of mergers and acquisitions, and describes the entire process from multiple angles such as premium mergers and acquisitions, performance compensation commitments, etc. Through case studies, guide students to think about the benefits and risks of premium mergers and acquisitions, as well as the application and impact of corporate mergers and acquisitions in strategic management and market expansion. At the same time, grasp the promoting role of performance compensation commitment agreements in the transaction process between both parties.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购动因理论；信息不对称理论；业绩补偿承诺；溢价并购；溢价并购风险；协同效应理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
